claim.claim-text:
1. An in vitro encapsulated cell indicator system comprising a culture vessel comprising:
(a) a first population of bone marrow stem cells (BMSCs) comprising an enhancer element selected from csx, bves, tie-2, von Willebrand, flk-1, ICAM-2, PPAR-γ2, TRAP, osteocalcin, CD11b, nestin, neurofilament, GFAP, myoD, SMHC, pdx-1, glucokinase, and α-fetoprotein enhancer elements, operably linked to a reporter gene;
(b) encapsulating material;
(c) a permeable membrane;

11. An in vitro encapsulated cell indicator system comprising a culture vessel comprising:
(a) a first population of embryonic stem cells (ES cells) comprising an enhancer element selected from csx, bves, tie-2, von Willebrand, flk-1, ICAM-2, PPAR-γ2, TRAP, osteocalcin, CD11b, nestin, neurofilament, GFAP, myoD, SMHC, pdx-1, glucokinase, and α-fetoprotein enhancer elements, operably linked to a reporter gene;
(b) encapsulating material;
(c) a permeable membrane;
